                "of 5 mbar of isobutane gas, was placed at the focal",
                "plane of Hybrid Recoil mass Analyzer (HIRA) to detect",
                "the evaporation residue."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two Silicon detectors were placed at",
                "15.5 degree, with respect to the beam direction in the",
                "horizontal plane, for absolute normalization of ER",
                "cross sections. A carbon foil with a thickness of",
                "10 ug/cm2 was placed 10 cm downstream from the target",
                "for equilibration."
              ]
            }
          ],
